  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792500/extras/eaa0c2763a0cc5586b30f2b1dfc14552.poster.avif?t=1737725744\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792500/extras/eaa0c2763a0cc5586b30f2b1dfc14552.webm?t=1737725744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792500/extras/eaa0c2763a0cc5586b30f2b1dfc14552.mp4?t=1737725744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792500/extras/7b12e22545c7ee2b4542a5e1ddb881b8.avif?t=1737725744\" width=600 height=222 /></span><br><br>Streets Ablaze is a 3D side-scrolling beat em' up inspired by the arcade and console games we played growing up.  Take control of one of the three heroes and hit the streets. Fight alongside a friend in this side-scrolling adventure.  Fight against cronies and minions, unleashing powerful combos and special attacks. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792500/extras/00fac1793e1c613522e60b348b03a3b2.poster.avif?t=1737725744\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792500/extras/00fac1793e1c613522e60b348b03a3b2.webm?t=1737725744\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/792500/extras/00fac1793e1c613522e60b348b03a3b2.mp4?t=1737725744\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Streets Ablaze takes you on a wild ride that spans different dimensions, eras, and environments. Chase down the evil Lord Blackhorn and battle a wide range of foes.<br><br><spa